snippet.title: Seed: Pre-Alpha Footage Teaser – An MMO Simulation
snippet.description:
Seed is a boundless journey for human survival, fuelled by discovery, collaboration, and genuine emotion. Experience some in-game, pre-Alpha footage of the project. 
Sign up to Seed here: http://bit.ly/join_seed

“The next step into a new world.”
An MMO Simulation by Klang. Powered by SpatialOS.

Music by Sveinbjörn Thorarensen.

All in-game footage is work in progress. 

– Follow the Seed Community --

Facebook: http://bit.ly/seed_facebook
Twitter: http://bit.ly/seed_twitter
Instagram: http://bit.ly/seed_instagram

Website: https://www.seed-online.com/
Dev Blog: https://www.seed-online.com/dev-blog
